Nihon Integround Holdings, Inc.

                    Nihon Integround Holdings, Inc. operates as a holding company with interests in providing civil engineering works. The company engages in underground pipe jacking, construction of prestressed concrete bridges & tanks, and land development activities. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan.                  




